Package org.jcvi.jillion.fasta.aa

This package deals with Fasta files that contain ProteinSequence data.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ProteinFastaDataStore
    ProteinFastaDataStore is a marker interface for FastaDataStores of ProteinFastaRecords.
    ProteinFastaFileDataStore  
    ProteinFastaRecord
    AminoAcidSequenceFastaRecord is an interface for FastaRecord objects using the ProteinSequence.
    ProteinFastaWriter  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractProteinFastaRecordVisitor
    AbstractProteinFastaRecordVisitor is an abstract implementation of FastaRecordVisitor that will collect the visit methods for a single fasta record and build an instance of ProteinFastaRecord.
    ProteinFastaFileDataStoreBuilder
    ProteinFastaFileDataStoreBuilder is a Builder that can create new instances of ProteinFastaDataStores using data from a given input fasta file.
    ProteinFastaRecordBuilder
    ProteinFastaRecordBuilder is a Builder class that makes instances of ProteinFastaRecords.
    ProteinFastaWriterBuilder
    ProteinFastaWriterBuilder is a Builder class that will create a new instance of ProteinFastaWriter that will write amino acid (protein) data to the given File or OutputStream.

Package org.jcvi.jillion.fasta.aa Description

This package deals with Fasta files that contain ProteinSequence data.
